      "para_id": "Q000962.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) For Inana , the lady of the E-ana , his lady , Šulgi , the powerful man , king of Urim , king of Sumer and Akkad , restored the E-ana , ( and ) built its great wall ."
